---------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| Test Case ID | Test case name                                  | Description                                                                                                      | Input                      | Expected output                           |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC001        | Function handles empty string input             | The calculator should return 0 when an empty string is passed.                                                   | ""                         | 0                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | ""                         | 0                                          |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC002        | Function handles single number input            | The calculator should return the same number when a single number is passed.                                     | "1"                        | 1                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "25"                       | 25                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC003        | Function handles two numbers separated by commas| The calculator should return the sum of two numbers separated by a comma.                                        | "1,2"                      | 3                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "15,30"                    | 45                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC004        | Function handles unknown number of inputs       | The calculator should return the sum of an unknown number of numbers separated by commas.                        | "1,2,3,4"                  | 10                                         |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "10,20,30,40"              | 100                                        |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC005        | Function handles newlines between numbers       | The calculator should allow newlines as valid delimiters along with commas and return the sum of the numbers.    | "1\n2,3"                   | 6                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "4\n5\n6"                  | 15                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC006        | Function handles invalid format                 | The calculator should return an error when a comma is immediately followed by a newline.                         | "1,\n"                     | Error                                      |
|              | (comma followed by newline)                     |                                                                                                                  | "2,\n3"                    | Error                                      |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC007        | Function handles custom delimiters              | The calculator should support a custom delimiter specified in the format "//[delimiter]\n" and return the sum.   | "//;\n1;2"                 | 3                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "//***\n3***4***5"         | 12                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC008        | Function handles custom delimiters of any length| The calculator should support delimiters of any length in the format "//[delimiter]\n" and return the correct sum.| "//[***]\n1***2***3"       | 6                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "//[###]\n10###20###30"    | 60                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC009        | Function handles negative numbers               | The calculator should throw an exception with a message indicating the negative number(s) in the input.          | "1,-2,3"                   | Exception: "negatives not allowed: -2"     |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "2,-3,-4"                  | Exception: "negatives not allowed: -3, -4" |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC010        | Function should ignore numbers larger than 1000 | The calculator should ignore numbers larger than 1000 when calculating the sum.                                  | "2,1001"                   | 2                                          |
|              |                                                 |                                                                                                                  | "1000,999,1001"            | 1999                                       |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| TC011        | Function handles combination of delimiters,     | The calculator should handle inputs that use commas, newlines, and custom delimiters together.                   | "//;\n1;2\n3"              | 6                                          |
|              | numbers, and newlines                           |                                                                                                                  | "//[***]\n10***20\n30"     | 60                                         |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
